//Light Color/Brightness
Color LEDColor "Hue" <lights>  ["Lighting"]
Switch LightsOn "Lights" ["Lighting"]
Dimmer DimmerDevice "Dimmer"


//Changing Light Speeds
Switch IsFlashing "Flashing" <switches> ["Switchable"]
Dimmer FlashSpeed
Switch IsFading "Fading" <switches> ["Switchable"]
Dimmer FadeSpeed

//Room Modes (Called switches but are really buttons that only receive ON command)
Switch NormalMode "Normal Mode" <modes> ["Switchable"]
Switch PartyMode "Party Mode" <modes> ["Switchable"]
Switch SleepMode "Sleep Mode" <modes> ["Switchable"]
Switch AlarmMode "Alarm Mode" <modes> ["Switchable"]
Switch ExitMode "Exit Mode" <modes> ["Switchable"]


Switch Monitors 

Switch BroadcastDevices "Broadcast Devices" ["Switchable"]

Dimmer EchoVolume
